(69, 'Modern Times', 'A bumbling tramp desires to build a home with a young woman, yet is thwarted time and time again by his lack of experience and habit of being in the wrong place at the wrong time..', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//7uoiKOEjxBBW0AgDGQWrlfGQ90w.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//kSlO1pHpwQfPQdgVPr7dJiJNtJ8.jpg', 141, 1936),
