(179, 'Red Beard', 'Aspiring to an easy job as personal physician to a wealthy family, Noboru Yasumoto is disappointed when his first post after medical school takes him to a small country clinic under the gruff doctor Red Beard. Yasumoto rebels in numerous ways, but Red Beard proves a wise and patient teacher. He gradually introduces his student to the unglamorous side of the profession, ultimately assigning him to care for a prostitute rescued from a local brothel.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//fo800fRcWtl3Zhs6tPHfXP4KBak.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//i4XlRFhNi61C2SZwgEuw8QgN59Q.jpg', 127, 1965),
