(361, 'The General', 'During America’s Civil War, Union spies steal engineer Johnny Gray''s beloved locomotive, ''The General''—with Johnnie''s lady love aboard an attached boxcar—and he single-handedly must do all in his power to both get The General back and to rescue Annabelle.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//nIp4gIXogCjfB1QABNsWwa9gSca.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//dYocWQoWk3Y6vBa0pGc0OQ8GLqn.jpg', 159, 1926),
