(546, 'The Boy in the Striped Pyjamas', 'When his family moves from their home in Berlin to a strange new house in Poland, young Bruno befriends Shmuel, a boy who lives on the other side of the fence where everyone seems to be wearing striped pajamas. Unaware of Shmuel''s fate as a Jewish prisoner or the role his own Nazi father plays in his imprisonment, Bruno embarks on a dangerous journey inside the camp''s walls.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//sLwYSEVVV3r047cjrpRAbGgNsfL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//sIZQA3FrXdVR5E6M3ctrAqitiQS.jpg', 149, 2008),
