(652, 'Back to the Future Part II', 'Marty and Doc are at it again as the time-traveling duo head to 2015 to nip some McFly family woes in the bud. But things go awry thanks to bully Biff Tannen and a pesky sports almanac. In a last-ditch attempt to set things straight, Marty finds himself bound for 1955 and face to face with his teenage parents -- again.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//YBawEsTkUZBDajKbd5LiHkmMGf.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//su0cmtK55eKXq0QjW68LQslUhUY.jpg', 127, 1989),
