(773, 'Pride', 'In 1984, a group of LGBT activists decide to raise money to support the National Union of Mineworkers during their lengthy strike. There is only one problem: the Union seems embarrassed to receive their support.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//mrITqHNw0XzT7egAPByDuiE3QZf.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//1tqzKtAWMRURxPTvs1hzcSOoKxe.jpg', 144, 2014),
(774, 'Hiroshima Mon Amour', 'The deep conversation between a Japanese architect and a French actress forms the basis of this celebrated French film, considered one of the vanguard productions of the French New Wave. Set in Hiroshima after the end of World War II, the couple -- lovers turned friends -- recount, over many hours, previous romances and life experiences. The two intertwine their stories about the past with pondering the devastation wrought by the atomic bomb dropped on the city.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//vjP7eX9c0xUD5i5dTRaP3NYC8iN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//4fynFAYPPYCkyIdt0bsCwWn3Hxv.jpg', 136, 1959),
(775, 'Azur & Asmar: The Princes'' Quest', 'Raised on tales of a Djinn fairy princess, Azur, a young Frenchman goes to North Africa in search of the sprite, only to discover that his close childhood friend, Asmar, an Arab youth whose mother raised both boys also seeks the genie.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ezkzULav0JxvLS5JOnQcjbUmfWO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//tykN4mGZha873vSln1zLU7NBHb3.jpg', 159, 2006),
(776, 'The Incredibles', 'Bob Parr has given up his superhero days to log in time as an insurance adjuster and raise his three children with his formerly heroic wife in suburbia. But when he receives a mysterious assignment, it''s time to get back into costume.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//2LqaLgk4Z226KkgPJuiOQ58wvrm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//se5Hxz7PArQZOG3Nx2bpfOhLhtV.jpg', 172, 2004),
(777, 'The Maltese Falcon', 'A private detective takes on a case that involves him with three eccentric criminals, a beautiful liar, and their quest for a priceless statuette.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//bf4o6Uzw5wqLjdKwRuiDrN1xyvl.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9xzVKUGbVKrrgwlmshJ8SxI5mL7.jpg', 160, 1941),
