(790, 'A Million Miles Away', 'The life of engineer and former NASA astronaut José M. Hernández, the first migrant farmworker to go to space.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//kMI3tgxLAZbzGOVlorUBva0kriS.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//23HvwdsAQeL0MxN9fm3d8m1NaPw.jpg', 178, 2023),
