(877, 'Berserk: The Golden Age Arc III - The Advent', 'A year has passed since Guts parted ways with the Band of the Hawks. Meanwhile, his former mercenary group is plotting a rescue mission to save an imprisoned Griffith.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//8VpZDCws3lwrR8RHlPOn7lLeQXS.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//mrVUkTJHY8MeZRvBDxxmnAhRcxa.jpg', 150, 2013),
(878, 'Cast Away', 'Chuck Nolan, a top international manager for FedEx, and Kelly, a Ph.D. student, are in love and heading towards marriage. Then Chuck''s plane to Malaysia crashes at sea during a terrible storm. He''s the only survivor, and finds himself marooned on a desolate island. With no way to escape, Chuck must find ways to survive in his new home.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//7lLJgKnAicAcR5UEuo8xhSMj18w.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ioqaIhJSkwa9DGRHGtOOUTiGRs2.jpg', 138, 2000),
(879, 'The Last Picture Show', 'High school seniors and best friends, Sonny and Duane, live in a dying Texas town. The handsome Duane is dating a local beauty, while Sonny is having an affair with the coach''s wife. As graduation nears and both boys contemplate their futures, Duane eyes the army and Sonny takes over a local business. Each struggles to figure out if he can escape this dead-end town and build a better life somewhere else.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//7NYePZc0lZrRomtmQsjOJMePTEb.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//fvmbYtOzQJqj0Y60UwyIB9iAaMD.jpg', 147, 1971),
(880, '12 Angry Men', 'During the trial of a man accused of his father''s murder, a lone juror takes a stand against the guilty verdict handed down by the others as a result of their preconceptions and prejudices.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//whDdYx3lh1LHTN0VlPFt51fX29g.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//rTf1rucbSn8IaW4AU11lvBk3JmX.jpg', 127, 1997),
(881, 'Primal Fear', 'An arrogant, high-powered attorney takes on the case of a poor altar boy found running away from the scene of the grisly murder of the bishop who has taken him in. The case gets a lot more complex when the accused reveals that there may or may not have been a third person in the room.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//qJf2TzE8nRTFbFMPJNW6c8mI0KU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//a4f6y7gbMmMLrwzJZrwmcNmEBM1.jpg', 168, 1996),
(882, 'Three Colors: Blue', 'The wife of a famous composer survives a car accident that kills her husband and daughter. Now alone, she shakes off her old identity and explores her newfound freedom but finds that she is unbreakably bound to other humans, including her husband’s mistress, whose existence she never suspected.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//33wsWxzsNstI8N7dvuwzFmj1qBd.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//y9N5tFCxCi2AIedOhU3OrVMfL2d.jpg', 153, 1993),
(883, 'Cat on a Hot Tin Roof', 'An alcoholic ex-football player drinks his days away, having failed to come to terms with his sexuality and his real feelings for his football buddy who died after an ambiguous accident. His wife is crucified by her desperation to make him desire her: but he resists the affections of his wife. His reunion with his father—who is dying of cancer—jogs a host of memories and revelations for both father and son.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//reO2NXIYPeBqehTsmia0P9rSMDv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//3Yz8IcUBPZ8zDff0ktHZk24Rot0.jpg', 157, 1958),
