(1142, 'Dragon Ball Z: Bardock - The Father of Goku', 'Bardock, Son Goku''s father, is a low-ranking Saiyan soldier who was given the power to see into the future by the last remaining alien on a planet he just destroyed. He witnesses the destruction of his race and must now do his best to stop Frieza''s impending massacre.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//docwOsWZuwJKQdwcYJtQPBcg6bm.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//gt2bAEykImRbsDLxjr5yts62aoq.jpg', 158, 1990),
