(1151, 'A Few Good Men', 'When cocky military lawyer Lt. Daniel Kaffee and his co-counsel, Lt. Cmdr. JoAnne Galloway, are assigned to a murder case, they uncover a hazing ritual that could implicate high-ranking officials such as shady Col. Nathan Jessep.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//rLOk4z9zL1tTukIYV56P94aZXKk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//8UOdqhVP28OcnzNL6DnQf0GDLvR.jpg', 179, 1992),
