(1286, 'Barbie: Princess Charm School', 'Barbie stars as Blair Willows, a kind-hearted girl who is chosen to attend Princess Charm School: a magical, modern place that teaches dancing, how to have tea parties, and proper princess manners. Blair loves her classes -- as well as the helpful magical sprites and her new friends, Princesses Hadley and Isla. But when royal teacher Dame Devin discovers that Blair looks a lot like the kingdom’s missing princess, she turns Blair’s world upside down to stop her from claiming the throne. Now Blair, Hadley and Delancy must find an enchanted crown to prove Blair’s true identity in this charming and magical princess story!', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//lI2jPbssax6XX5vDqB9mTJHGzfH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//pR51tWHlUWUEnPUc5my9anqcDto.jpg', 147, 2011),
(1287, 'Days of Heaven', 'In 1916, a Chicago steel worker accidentally kills his supervisor and flees to the Texas panhandle with his girlfriend and little sister to work harvesting wheat in the fields of a stoic farmer.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//siE1XQ544MLO27geLYDbUDy3oTt.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9Upbup1xrQuTDbspIh9aytEH5xA.jpg', 154, 1978),
(1288, 'Johnny Got His Gun', 'A young American soldier, rendered in pseudocoma from an artillery shell from WWI, recalls his life leading up to that point.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ryIY3FPmTtXu9g6W4I69qCdkxKj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//cnf41Zu7ue1VgYdJEIYRC9w5yhS.jpg', 120, 1971),
(1289, 'Devdas', 'In 1900s India, Calcuttan zamindar Devdas Mukherjee — unable to marry his lover — takes up alcohol and the company of a courtesan to alleviate the pain.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//dUBFi7bnLRfm4WaTh4ZoF2tbBJj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//iYawbkoQmHCdnyR5bVB9XBQS90j.jpg', 153, 2002),
(1290, 'Au Revoir les Enfants', 'Au revoir les enfants tells a heartbreaking story of friendship and devastating loss concerning two boys living in Nazi-occupied France. At a provincial Catholic boarding school, the precocious youths enjoy true camaraderie—until a secret is revealed. Based on events from writer-director Malle’s own childhood, the film is a subtle, precisely observed tale of courage, cowardice, and tragic awakening.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//lXP90Vx7OcviBfbbokcaG6zVnPG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//mQC9OxFBGKJmk4tgzpmKO1nIZx5.jpg', 177, 1987),
(1291, 'The Valet', 'World famous movie star Olivia faces a PR disaster when a paparazzi snaps a photo of her with her married lover, Vincent. The hard-working valet Antonio accidentally appears in the same photo and is enlisted to pose as Olivia’s new boyfriend as a cover-up. This ruse with Olivia thrusts Antonio into the spotlight and unexpected chaos.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//q7FmdJHKMLIC4XgWfcFRIu2iVdL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//kB1Qrsg189eDz4Ej3ABXtLudClq.jpg', 131, 2022),
(1292, 'The Lighthouse', 'Two lighthouse keepers try to maintain their sanity while living on a remote and mysterious New England island in the 1890s.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//f1tIYarTbkBdIT1aW0gzelDwknv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//sYLzRuEcwSz0L1Z92wQNrETHU9O.jpg', 150, 2019),
(1293, 'Love Don''t Co$t a Thing', 'A high school outcast pays a cheerleader to pose as his girlfriend so he can be considered cool.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//88zspc72LIkfiuMnGpHnsWCuqEH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//bYk4H2MSvNWckhrYhZNQHe8v90o.jpg', 153, 2003),
(1294, 'Fist of Legend', 'Chen Zhen, a Chinese engineering student in Kyoto, who braves the insults and abuse of his Japanse fellow students for his local love Mitsuko Yamada, daughter of the director, returns in 1937 to his native Shangai, under Japanse protectorate -in fact military occupation- after reading about the death of his kung-fu master Hou Ting-An in a fight against the Japanese champion Ryuichi Akutagawa.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//Aqa1Yuog2OFrduwSffxZc2w4Tnk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//duJgP9voxAfO7ohgeaYvDNFIoUu.jpg', 127, 1994),
(1295, 'Training Day', 'On his first day on the job as a narcotics officer, a rookie cop works with a rogue detective who isn''t what he appears.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//bUeiwBQdupBLQthMCHKV7zv56uv.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//nuO8o9ltxhI7AZQxePavEZ4TyHa.jpg', 163, 2001),
(1296, 'Walk the Line', 'A chronicle of country music legend Johnny Cash''s life, from his early days on an Arkansas cotton farm to his rise to fame with Sun Records in Memphis, where he recorded alongside Elvis Presley, Jerry Lee Lewis and Carl Perkins.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//zMkD6FVikyPNnigoupO7vD5ti9p.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//pMBKzEotLUzk3NuQiyVjZEDlH70.jpg', 130, 2005),
(1297, 'The Quiet Girl', 'A quiet, neglected girl is sent away from her dysfunctional family to live with relatives for the summer. She blossoms in their care, but in this house where there are meant to be no secrets, she discovers one.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//6Njyz53N417cgxE0d7cBEWHUEjc.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//23jok5sYloPEBwKd6Bp4V8Y1O9I.jpg', 140, 2022),
(1298, 'Shadow of a Doubt', 'Just when Charlie is feeling especially frustrated by the lack of excitement in her small town in California, she receives wonderful news: Her uncle and namesake, Charlie, is coming to visit. However, as secrets about him come to the fore, her admiration turns into suspicion.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ptyWagbWE8jSGyV2tGEzAdVbRCj.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//lV4504ucv4Y0AtNMSrlgk7TwiIC.jpg', 164, 1943),
(1299, 'The Favourite', 'England, early 18th century. The close relationship between Queen Anne and Sarah Churchill is threatened by the arrival of Sarah''s cousin, Abigail Hill, resulting in a bitter rivalry between the two cousins to be the Queen''s favourite.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//cwBq0onfmeilU5xgqNNjJAMPfpw.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ph5fElfh4U7O3jwhFljxz2LDp1l.jpg', 137, 2018),
(1300, 'The Skin I Live In', 'A brilliant plastic surgeon creates a synthetic skin that withstands any kind of damage. His guinea pig: a mysterious and volatile woman who holds the key to his obsession.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//xa7uCwGYykrf8MMI8iF5dZvNlrG.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//qn8NzshtQmJD7Nm06sAp5yOtexH.jpg', 152, 2011);
INSERT INTO Contents (id, title, description, thumbnail_url, video_url, duration, release_year) VALUES
(1301, 'Somewhere in Time', 'Young writer Richard Collier is met on the opening night of his first play by an old lady who begs him to "Come back to me". Mystified, he tries to find out about her, and learns that she is a famous stage actress from the early 1900s. Becoming more and more obsessed with her, by self-hypnosis he manages to travel back in time—where he meets her.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//hmdegiSwVYUNvEfihaE3HRM3Sos.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//d7gEJYEookiF0SHPD8fMXcCgpC9.jpg', 141, 1980),
(1302, 'The 36th Chamber of Shaolin', 'The anti-Ching patriots, under the guidance of Ho Kuang-han, have secretly set up their base in Canton, disguised as school masters. During a brutal Manchu attack, Lui manages to escape, and devotes himself to learning the martial arts in order to seek revenge.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//6j1ZnapQPGD9aUcqQWqFYPhWd3B.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//4hRQylOUK1pUMtvalpJJsnxZffy.jpg', 144, 1978),
(1303, 'Almost Famous', 'In 1973, 15-year-old William Miller''s unabashed love of music and aspiration to become a rock journalist lands him an assignment from Rolling Stone magazine to interview and tour with the up-and-coming band, Stillwater.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//3rrkyLYbgLj84AYvjhdcJot4JPx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//xleIwr1wUlWqvFHaU1PItf0YLrZ.jpg', 120, 2000),
(1304, 'The Devils', 'In 17th-century France, Father Urbain Grandier seeks to protect the city of Loudun from the corrupt establishment of Cardinal Richelieu. Hysteria occurs within the city when he is accused of witchcraft by the sexually repressed Sister Jeanne.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//y1k7eiOFc6fzm8XeTa1kNGx6JIs.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//brA5IjnrSX2ElMgK1s0weiyDtrl.jpg', 126, 1971),
(1305, 'Little Big Man', 'Jack Crabb, looking back from extreme old age, tells of his life being raised by Indians and fighting with General Custer.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//pLvUVqadEI9cPrRlTru6ee71EWU.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//uuich47VwLn44B0gHmhgLt6hTcM.jpg', 123, 1970),
(1306, 'No Man''s Land', 'Two soldiers from opposite sites get stuck between the front lines in the same trench. The UN is asked to free them and both sides agree on a ceasefire, but will they stick to it?', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//jRffyv5gaJb6Sna1S6UMRCPHuso.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//e86j48mkpIzFSNutRGcNiltWCNt.jpg', 122, 2001),
(1307, 'Elvis', 'The life story of Elvis Presley as seen through the complicated relationship with his enigmatic manager, Colonel Tom Parker.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//qBOKWqAFbveZ4ryjJJwbie6tXkQ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//xyS0NgcQ2pbGWcwvSSu3xKEBhoO.jpg', 152, 2022),
(1308, 'Suspiria', 'An American newcomer to a prestigious German ballet academy comes to realize that the school is a front for something sinister amid a series of grisly murders.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//5ya8jTbNZTrCFUx9OwpNBjCivXY.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//j7rl2LphIbC88FppTfwJ5Gxj9kX.jpg', 168, 1977),
(1309, 'Hero', 'During China''s Warring States period, a district prefect arrives at the palace of Qin Shi Huang, claiming to have killed the three assassins who had made an attempt on the king''s life three years ago.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//1NBtOH3KPU9UUp1vzVHJ8qzdW88.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//jDz6RYN3nKYtlo7J9IMvGoJit7B.jpg', 156, 2002),
(1310, 'BlacKkKlansman', 'Colorado Springs, late 1970s. Ron Stallworth, an African American police officer, and Flip Zimmerman, his Jewish colleague, run an undercover operation to infiltrate the Ku Klux Klan.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//8jxqAvSDoneSKRczaK8v9X5gqBp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//gMVdhfQ7q9DFHhDkehrququjGPd.jpg', 154, 2018),
(1311, 'A Star Is Born', 'Seasoned musician Jackson Maine discovers — and falls in love with — struggling artist Ally. She has just about given up on her dream to make it big as a singer — until Jack coaxes her into the spotlight. But even as Ally''s career takes off, the personal side of their relationship is breaking down, as Jack fights an ongoing battle with his own internal demons.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//wrFpXMNBRj2PBiN4Z5kix51XaIZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//38IKiVWoqxRLpZawb6QWn1vIdLo.jpg', 126, 2018),
(1312, 'Boyhood', 'The film tells a story of a divorced couple trying to raise their young son. The story follows the boy for twelve years, from first grade at age 6 through 12th grade at age 17-18, and examines his relationship with his parents as he grows.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//2BvtvDUyxiMJ4dmKfiQf4qdOHQN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//mVH9yTLSk2g7RXkpmKCJ4HKijWX.jpg', 153, 2014),
(1313, 'Band of Outsiders', 'Cinephile slackers Franz and Arthur spend their days mimicking the antiheroes of Hollywood noirs and Westerns while pursuing the lovely Odile. The misfit trio upends convention at every turn, be it through choreographed dances in cafés or frolicsome romps through the Louvre. Eventually, their romantic view of outlaws pushes them to plan their own heist, but their inexperience may send them out in a blaze of glory -- which could be just what they want.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9oqyj79xmcypxLajJdefOtrYx64.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//kKsy8sCjfOtfHPBT2i8z13bIRij.jpg', 128, 1964),
(1314, 'How to Steal a Million', 'A woman must steal a statue from a Paris museum to help conceal her father''s art forgeries.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//dkCHsyFdyA63nUXzEvDvqNhqUuO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//jXPrGgk6PypAsv8IPq8NqlQi6ts.jpg', 148, 1966),
(1315, 'Rescued by Ruby', 'Chasing his dream to join an elite K-9 unit, a state trooper partners with a fellow underdog: clever but naughty shelter pup Ruby. Based on a true story.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//tPlJEodEn0SSV4avo8KSawtlTlN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//zQG1FYDqoWo2hYhE5GVZ1yrWSfh.jpg', 131, 2022),
(1316, 'Cyrano, My Love', 'Paris, France, December 1897. The young playwright Edmond Rostand feels like a failure. Inspiration has abandoned him. Married and father of two children, desperate and penniless, he persuades the great actor Constant Coquelin to perform the main role in his new play. But there is a problem: Coquelin wants to premiere it at Christmas and Edmond has not written a single word.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9Y1VxSfJdu8fqQqgX0x6OObxvUw.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//dn7wTIud3Yroopm8bWN8WtidTBW.jpg', 176, 2018),
(1317, 'Carol', 'In 1950s New York, a department-store clerk who dreams of a better life falls for an older, married woman.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//cJeled7EyPdur6TnCA5GYg0UVna.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//o0ghC4XMIMdbRBXIqSvnPrxwj3W.jpg', 161, 2015),
(1318, 'Hercules', 'Bestowed with superhuman strength, a young mortal named Hercules sets out to prove himself a hero in the eyes of his father, the great god Zeus. Along with his friends Pegasus, a flying horse, and Phil, a personal trainer, Hercules is tricked by the hilarious, hotheaded villain Hades, who''s plotting to take over Mount Olympus!', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//dK9rNoC97tgX3xXg5zdxFisdfcp.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//oG9dcGSSu13fjFp1Uly15ZXjRKV.jpg', 148, 1997),
(1319, 'The Rules of the Game', 'A weekend at a marquis’ country château lays bare some ugly truths about a group of haut bourgeois acquaintances.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//8JOzt7uFZyshcuzCBmYU6CDJL4D.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//eGn78oJms1vrE4Z38m05d5GSTvk.jpg', 178, 1939),
(1320, 'I Can Only Imagine', '10-year-old Bart Millard lives with his mother and abusive father Arthur in Texas. One day his mother drops him off at a Christian camp where he meets Shannon. Upon his return from camp, Bart finds his mother has left and movers are removing her belongings. He angrily confronts his father, who denies that his abusiveness was the reason she left. Years later, in high school, Bart and Shannon are dating. Bart plays football to please his father but is injured, breaking both ankles and ending his career. The only elective with openings is music class, so he reluctantly signs up.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//veZszwMZu8d3WMU6TJX9sV5w1Y4.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//AjtQdUX41skfo8tthtrnJZI9bXV.jpg', 168, 2018),
(1321, 'The Insult', 'After an emotional exchange between a Lebanese Christian and a Palestinian refugee escalates, the men end up in a court case that gets national attention.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//w9mlrckg3ZU2rsAlKUbLD1CgBTk.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//ekIdTKHLWzZ4ojDLEkzLzNb8ggK.jpg', 140, 2017),
(1322, 'The Name of the Rose', '14th-century Franciscan monk William of Baskerville and his young novice arrive at a conference to find that several monks have been murdered under mysterious circumstances. To solve the crimes, William must rise up against the Church''s authority and fight the shadowy conspiracy of monastery monks using only his intelligence; which is considerable.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//2BuVu0j6v2kNY2gGxtO3sDGyob2.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//2JB2nJQOBZ7Q9vAtzbha2YsqJbH.jpg', 150, 1986),
(1323, 'Tad, the Lost Explorer and the Emerald Tablet', 'Tad accidentally unleashes an ancient spell, endangering the lives of his friends Mummy, Jeff, and Belzoni. With everyone against him and only helped by Sara, he sets off on an adventure to end the Curse of the Mummy.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//jvIVl8zdNSOAJImw1elQEzxStMN.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//tUBN1paMQ1tmVA5Sjy1ZjPWVsiF.jpg', 159, 2022),
(1324, 'Balloon', 'Two families attempt a daredevil plan to escape the GDR with a homemade hot air balloon, but it crashes just before the border. The Stasi finds traces of this attempt to escape and immediately starts investigations, while the two families are forced to build a new escape balloon. With each passing day the Stasi is closer on their heels - a nerve-wracking race against time begins.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//nRs8A0zp0jU211j8Zay3ApIzlpx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//sKK1fb08uCcTc0w6PlVsx3BXJdg.jpg', 151, 2018),
(1325, 'You Can''t Take It with You', 'Alice, the only relatively normal member of the eccentric Sycamore family, falls in love with Tony Kirby, but his wealthy banker father and snobbish mother strongly disapprove of the match. When the Kirbys are invited to dinner to become better acquainted with their future in-laws, things don''t turn out the way Alice had hoped.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//9JltqbDyWstYW6gnvqDO6L5bOrx.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//As4GJO5V3SxbSDW8ZEWPnYtSZIg.jpg', 125, 1938),
(1326, 'To Sir, with Love', 'A British Guianese engineer starts a job as a high school teacher in London’s East End, where his uninterested and delinquent pupils are in desperate need of attention and care.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//xMaVwTfgETmPs5yp3lNK5SeWCtB.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//vUZbARc0xY3MjwZnZtybpqbAoK9.jpg', 153, 1967),
(1327, 'The Secret Life of Bees', 'Set in South Carolina in 1964, this is the tale of Lily Owens a 14 year-old girl who is haunted by the memory of her late mother. To escape her lonely life and troubled relationship with her father, Lily flees with Rosaleen, her caregiver and only friend, to a South Carolina town that holds the secret to her mother''s past.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//m1LGEeoYfc6crbfG8WmTKg9SVqL.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//3CcO4QdasRCitq2dczOpx7CXgLM.jpg', 137, 2008),
(1328, 'One, Two, Three', 'C.R. MacNamara is a managing director for Coca Cola in West Berlin during the Cold War, just before the Wall is put up. When Scarlett, the rebellious daughter of his boss, comes to West Berlin, MacNamara has to look after her, but this turns out to be a difficult task when she reveals to be married to a communist.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//yWQE227ub1frfnjP5HZy0wLF0wu.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//4safDVSZx7a4I1TQoSyz6E1agzM.jpg', 123, 1961),
(1329, 'Upgrade', 'A brutal mugging leaves Grey Trace paralyzed in the hospital and his beloved wife dead. A billionaire inventor soon offers Trace a cure — an artificial intelligence implant called STEM that will enhance his body. Now able to walk, Grey finds that he also has superhuman strength and agility — skills he uses to seek revenge against the thugs who destroyed his life.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//cF8fsHKGfqdlm7kdmG2Dub4E2rg.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//q9HocL5f8WwPldwpvmpk8ZaNZkC.jpg', 120, 2018),
(1330, 'Rogue One: A Star Wars Story', 'A rogue band of resistance fighters unite for a mission to steal the Death Star plans and bring a new hope to the galaxy.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//i0yw1mFbB7sNGHCs7EXZPzFkdA1.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//6t8ES1d12OzWyCGxBeDYLHoaDrT.jpg', 176, 2016),
(1331, 'My Dinner with Andre', 'Wally, a struggling playwright and actor, reluctantly agrees to catch up with his old friend Andre, a theater director who disappeared several years prior in order to travel the world. Meeting at a posh Manhattan restaurant, the two share life stories, anecdotes and philosophical musings over the course of an evening meal.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//u2KB70Xlzwg920mYWlGb18YIatd.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//h1ngZT7mWm5Moy4krWEUnlj0Ef.jpg', 164, 1981),
(1332, 'My Cousin Vinny', 'Two carefree pals from Brooklyn traveling through rural Alabama on their way back to college are mistakenly arrested, and charged with murder. Fortunately, one of them has a cousin who''s a lawyer - Vincent Gambini, a former auto mechanic from Brooklyn who just passed his bar exam after his sixth try. When he arrives with his leather-clad girlfriend, to try his first case, it''s a real shock - for him and the Deep South!', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//iwSURa8nS2ujwrU3s1lfxxX7voH.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//uEoaOfvWibpvjBNxFoj4MxWn0OH.jpg', 143, 1992),
(1333, 'The French Connection', 'Tough narcotics detective ''Popeye'' Doyle is in hot pursuit of a suave French drug dealer who may be the key to a huge heroin-smuggling operation.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//5XSGvIKl2yPvOkieFjc3rzLw7x0.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//AsaW2VwcArvQmYjf2wsDjqWEn6f.jpg', 133, 1971),
(1334, 'About Fate', 'Two strangers believe in love but never seem to be able to find its true meaning. In a wild twist of events, fate puts each in the other''s path on one stormy New Year''s Eve.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//fabZkaVHYJ67KbZx7oFoitauX34.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//30COvn7g7PP58wBkrnnh7Ws9bJS.jpg', 175, 2022),
(1335, 'I Lost My Body', 'A story of Naoufel, a young man who is in love with Gabrielle. In another part of town, a severed hand escapes from a dissection lab, determined to find its body again.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//z5dXCywyo8zEPNDkeQY7nbvkrz8.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//rHJX9CMYk7FXxUV5la1dEFSPVCv.jpg', 142, 2019),
(1336, 'All Three of Us', 'An Iranian family survives the shah and the ayatollah and moves to France. This story follows the family through it all. Despite the politics, revolution, prison, beatings, assassinations and suicides this is a comedy.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//aPYtRdJwt85OgZIUBZ5tHgmfyCO.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//wncuCwPGYWbsLzv00frxCjh10e2.jpg', 152, 2015),
(1337, 'Ghostbusters', 'After losing their academic posts at a prestigious university, a team of parapsychologists goes into business as proton-pack-toting "ghostbusters" who exterminate ghouls, hobgoblins and supernatural pests of all stripes. An ad campaign pays off when a knockout cellist hires the squad to purge her swanky digs of demons that appear to be living in her refrigerator.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//7E8nLijS9AwwUEPu2oFYOVKhdFA.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//c6yfABGVKuB5cjoOwdX4AJMlzUz.jpg', 166, 1984),
(1338, 'The Book Thief', 'While subjected to the horrors of WWII Germany, young Liesel finds solace by stealing books and sharing them with others. Under the stairs in her home, a Jewish refugee is being sheltered by her adoptive parents.', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//wj4U5sMLcJMa3WR9CpRR9e2sdgZ.jpg', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500//arFPEDEW4PzPaMBXgTPzJlumfGw.jpg', 164, 2013),
